  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      25 patients, treated by brachytherapy in a phase II study &quot;Mammosite&quot; (from 2003 to 2005),
      will be asked to attend a clinical exam in order to evaluate the late cutaneous toxicity due
      to brachytherapy.

      During this consultation, a blood sample will be taken for analysis ( rate of CD8
      T-Lymphocyte Apoptosis)
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
